# Introduction

One of my learning goals was to build an end-to-end enterprise AI platform on Microsoft Azure using cloud-native technologies rather than deploying a simple containerized application.

Instead of relying on Azure Portal, I wanted to provision and manage the entire environment using the Azure CLI. This approach helped me better understand Azure services, automate infrastructure provisioning, and make the deployment repeatable.

The project combines modern DevOps, Kubernetes, AI, and cloud networking concepts into a single production-style platform.

